@@TJvStringGrid.SortGrid@Integer@Boolean@Boolean@TJvSortType@Boolean
Description:
Call this method to sort the grid.

Parameters:
Column:
is the index of the column you want to use for the sort
Ascending: 
is the way you want to sort. Ascending or Descending.
Fixed: 
is true if you also want to sort fixed rows.
BlankTop: 
is true if blank cells are moved to top on ascending and to bottom on descending. This may be usefull if cells may be blank for numerical datas!.

