@@TJvSortType
Description:
This is the different types of sorts available in the TJvStringGrid. 

* stAutomatic if you want the component to find the type by himself 
* stClassic if you want to use a non case sensitive sort 
* stCaseSensitive if you want to use a case sensitive sort 
* stNumeric if you want to use a numeric sort 
* stDate if you want to use a date/time sort 
* stCurrency if you want to use a currency sort

